      "d715084a-a3c5-453c-bc7d-56bfbd5f63cd/jipipe:algorithm:pass-through" : {
        "pinned" : true,
        "name" : "Pass through",
        "description" : "If enabled, the algorithm will pass the input data directly to the output data without any processing. This is different from enabling/disabling the algorithm as this will not disable dependent algorithms.\nPlease note that setting this parameter via adaptive parameters (if available) does not always yield the expected result. The reason behind this is that pass-through is not trivial for certain nodes. We recommend to use a split node if node execution should be made adaptive."
      },
