        "description" : "Array of Z indices to be included in the final image. All indices begin with zero. Indices outside the available range are automatically wrapped. Return an empty array to skip a slice.\n\nThe format is the following: [range];[range];... with [range] either being a single integer or a range [from]-[to] (both inclusive). Negative values must be enclosed in parentheses. Example: 0-5;1;(-1)-10. If you want more customization options use the expression mode and functions such as MAKE_SEQUENCE."
